---
title: Grilled Vietnamese-Inspired Hoisin Pork Wraps with Mint-Cucumber Salsa, Sriracha Mayo and Peanuts
description: Sticky, sweet grilled hoisin-glazed pork chops are thinly sliced before getting stuffed in tortillas for a fusion of flavours! The refreshing cucumber-mint salsa brightens and lightens while the creamy sriracha-mayo adds some heat to every mouth-watering bite!
